      <scopecontent id="aspace_d38f8ba73fc39922266b38a3a3edcf38">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of files of Philip K. Bondy, professor in the Yale School of Medicine, concerning the Department of Internal Medicine; Yale's relation to the Veteran's Administration Hospital in West Haven, Connecticut; and other administrative matters.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
